New group with user

1. Rosetta goes to /group/ and makes a new group
2. Rosetta clicks Add Member, and enters the name Sakua, leaves the rest blank/default
3. Rosetta sends the Sakua link to sakua@blackstar.com
4. Sakua fills in the RSS and type information
5. Sakua follows the instructions to authenticate the group
6. Sakua subscribes to the RSS feed on the user page
